    "description": "Natco Pharma South Asia Partners has an exciting opening for a Surgeon at our Visakhapatnam office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Natco Pharma South Asia Partners:\nNatco Pharma South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Adhere to NABH/JCI accreditation standards\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Natco Pharma South Asia Partners!",
